item.title: Serverfiles
item.description: Serverfiles What is special about this files? Nothing! Everything we did, you can do with enough work, time and effort. Why should you use this files? To create your own project on a safe and modern base. To start developing your own systems. What do you get? A clean state of the game based on latest v3. Local developing environment. Client, Client-Source, Server-Source, Mysql-Portable, Packer-Source, Dumper-Source. Discount on all our systems and services.
